# WorldCupIQ AI — Environment configuration
#
# The FIFA World Cup 2026 challenge requires these exact variable names.
# Do NOT rename or alias them.
#
# In the Lovable managed environment, LOVABLE_API_KEY is auto-provisioned
# and routes model traffic through the Lovable AI Gateway; it satisfies
# the GEMINI_API_KEY role at runtime. When self-hosting on Cloud Run or
# Colab, populate the challenge variables directly with your Google keys.

# --- Reasoning & agents ---
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# --- Real-time information ---
SEARCH_API_KEY=your_search_api_key_here
AIMODE_API_KEY=your_ai_mode_api_key_here
LOCAL_API_KEY=your_local_services_api_key_here

# --- Geospatial ---
MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here

# --- Optional: Lovable-managed routing (auto-set inside Lovable) ---
# LOVABLE_API_KEY=lovable_managed